Subject: scsi: libcxgbi: find cxgbi device by MAC address
Git-commit: ffcd686b913eab35b7f447d8e373aae16d5fed34
Patch-mainline: v5.2-rc1
References: bsc#1136352 jsc#SLE-4687

If cxgbi_device_find_by_netdev() returns NULL then find cxgbi device by MAC
address.

